### **Template Auto-Detection & Registration**

#### **1. Template Detection** (`src/llama-chat.cpp`, lines 87-233)
The `llm_chat_detect_template()` function uses pattern matching on template strings:

**Mistral Family Detection** (lines 103-137):
```cpp
if (tmpl.find("mistral") == 0 || tmpl_contains("[INST]")) {
    if (tmpl_contains("[SYSTEM_PROMPT]")) {
        return LLM_CHAT_TEMPLATE_MISTRAL_V7;  // v7 template
    } else if (tmpl_contains("[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]") || tmpl_contains("' [INST] '")) {
        // v1, v3, v3-tekken detection
